title: 'Anthropic provider: parse thinking content blocks in SSE stream'
---
In provider_anthropic.ml complete_streaming: detect content_block_start with type=thinking, emit ThinkingDelta on content_block_delta with type=thinking_delta.

ALSO required (not in separate task — do here):
- Add `thinking_budget_tokens: int option` to runtime_config.ml provider_config (default None)
- Update config_loader.ml provider_config JSON parser (line ~46, the provider_config constructor) to parse "thinking_budget_tokens" key
- Include `"thinking": {"type":"enabled","budget_tokens":N}` in Anthropic request body when Some n; omit otherwise

Acceptance criteria:
- Config with thinking_budget_tokens set sends correct Anthropic API request body
- ThinkingDelta events appear in SSE stream when provider is Anthropic + thinking enabled
- `make test` passes (add at least one unit test for the SSE parser path)